# Code ownership for provide-io/ci-tooling

# Global ownership - all files require review from maintainers
* @provide-io/maintainers

# Actions require additional infrastructure team review
/actions/ @provide-io/infrastructure @provide-io/maintainers

# Workflows require additional infrastructure team review
/workflows/ @provide-io/infrastructure @provide-io/maintainers

# Scripts and automation
/scripts/ @provide-io/infrastructure

# Documentation can be reviewed by docs team
/docs/ @provide-io/docs @provide-io/maintainers
README.md @provide-io/docs @provide-io/maintainers

# Configuration files require infrastructure review
/.github/ @provide-io/infrastructure
pyproject.toml @provide-io/infrastructure
*.yml @provide-io/infrastructure
*.yaml @provide-io/infrastructure